item.title: How do i change home in Delta-Scape?
item.dc:creator: @Rog3r Rog3r
item.description:
@Rog3r wrote:

Although you are right, he posted here to get help; not taunted.

But you can most likely do the command: ::mypos when you start, and then remember the X axis number.
Then in Player.java, search for it and you can change it. [For starting place]

Or, in Client.java search for it and change it accordingly.

Same with the X axis.
